        "R3 interface: Serial0/1/0 address 10.0.0.9/30 (link to R1)"
      ],
      "confidence": 0.95
    },
    {
      "type": "Intermediate device unreachable / unknown state (router2)",
      "cause": "Router2's configuration and operational state could not be obtained (management connection failed) and its interfaces were not discovered; if 172.16.0.12 is located via R2 this device being down/unreachable would contribute to the failure.",
