  "target": null,
  "needs_fix": true,
  "plan": {
    "problem": "Mutual static routes on router1 and router3 for 172.16.0.0/24 (each pointing at the other) create a forwarding loop/blackhole, preventing reachability to 172.16.0.12.",
    "fix_summary": "Remove the incorrect static route on router3 that points 172.16.0.0/24 at router1 (next-hop 10.0.0.10). Risk: traffic to 172.16.0.0/24 may be temporarily unreachable until a correct route to the network (via router2) is installed or router2 is confirmed reachable. Assumption: router2 is the correct path to 172.16.0.0/24 and will be handled separately if needed.",
